rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0001
rows.name: That was quite a grand funeral...

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0002
rows.name:
It truly showed how deeply Fan-sama
was loved by her people.

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0003
rows.name:
There's no one who could truly
fill the role of Acedia's Goddess,
I fear.

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0004
rows.name:
So, Rex,
what's your plan now?

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0005
rows.name:
We'll need His Holiness Marveni's help
to reach the World Tree, but...

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0007
rows.name:
His Holiness Marveni
has requested your presence.
He awaits you in the audience chamber.

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0008
rows.name:
That's great timing!
Maybe he wants to discuss
the World Tree?

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0010
rows.name: We shall find out when we go there.

rows.label: fev06_110_125_msg0011
rows.name:
Well then, let's head on over
to the audience chamber.
